By plant and material, get data for the below 3 tables:-
SO Demand => VBBE-MBDAT [Mat.Avail.Date ]– >plant/material/date
Dep Demand => RESB-BDTER [Reqmts date] -– >plant/material/date
Ind Forecast => MDPB-PDATU [Finish date ]– >plant/material/date
Union all date from the above table.
Sort by date, get the first record date.
